result.title: MindSweeper-7, Coding Contest by Programming Club IIIT Jabalpur
result.content:
Hello everyone,
Programming Club IIIT Jabalpur is conducting MindSweeper-7 on 21 Feb from 4:00 P.M. to 6:00 P.M. It's an open contest and everyone is invited to participate. The contest consists of 5 easy-medium level problems to be solved in 2 hours. The contest will be a good exposure to competitive coding for beginners. Register for the challenge here .
